{"type":"message","id":"53611a6f","parentId":"968e5471","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:47:16.269Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what skills are installed. Let me check the available skills listed in the system prompt and also check if there are any skills installed in the workspace.\n\nFrom the system prompt, I can see these skills:\n1. feishu-bitable\n2. feishu-calendar\n3. feishu-channel-rules\n4. feishu-create-doc\n5. feishu-fetch-doc\n6. feishu-im-read\n7. feishu-task\n8. feishu-troubleshoot\n9. feishu-update-doc\n10. clawhub\n11. coding-agent\n12. gemini\n13. github\n14. healthcheck\n15. node-connect\n16. skill-creator\n17. summarize\n18. weather\n19. vibesurf\n20. Agent Browser\n21. multi-search-engine\n22. self-improvement\n23. skill-vetter\n24. tiktok_scout\n25. tts_hair_scout\n\nLet me also check what's in the workspace skills directory.","thinkingSignature":"b3c85b35e3137f03cb52591debbd616543f11b5adaf3f0fddb80a5ac6a097f95"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n目前安装的 Skill 挺多的，列一下主要的：\n\n**飞书相关（已加载）**\n- `feishu-bitable` — 多维表格管理\n- `feishu-calendar` — 日历和日程\n- `feishu-create-doc` — 创建云文档\n- `feishu-fetch-doc` — 获取文档内容\n- `feishu-im-read` — 读取消息、搜索聊天记录\n- `feishu-task` — 任务管理\n- `feishu-update-doc` — 更新云文档\n- `feishu-troubleshoot` — 飞书问题排查\n\n**常用工具**\n- `clawhub` — 搜索/安装社区 Skill\n- `coding-agent` — 编码任务（可调用 Codex/Claude Code）\n- `github` — GitHub 操作\n- `gemini` — Gemini CLI\n- `weather` — 天气查询\n- `summarize` — 总结 URL/文件/网页\n- `vibesurf` — 浏览器自动化\n- `multi-search-engine` — 多引擎搜索\n\n**其他**\n- `healthcheck` — 安全审计\n- `node-connect` — 设备连接诊断\n- `skill-creator` — 创建/优化 Skill\n- `tiktok_scout` / `tts_hair_scout` — TikTok 相关\n\n需要我帮你了解某个 Skill 的具体用法吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":118,"output":520,"cacheRead":34763,"cacheWrite":606,"totalTokens":36007,"cost":{"input":0.0000354,"output":0.000624,"cacheRead":0.0020857799999999998,"cacheWrite":