{"type":"message","id":"6ab05b52","parentId":"dedcab87","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:31:49.917Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_18gao2b1wvz6_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_user_message, feishu_im_user_fetch_resource, feishu_im_user_get_messages, feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages, feishu_im_user_search_messages\n[plugins] feishu_search: Registered feishu_search_doc_wiki\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive_file, feishu_doc_comments, feishu_doc_media\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki_space, feishu_wiki_space_node\n[plugins] feishu_sheets: Registered feishu_sheet\n[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_bot_image\n[plugins] Registered all OAPI tools (calendar, task, bitable, search, drive, wiki, sheets, im)\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_fetch_doc, feishu_create_doc, feishu_update_doc\n[plugins] feishu_oauth: Registered feishu_oauth tool\n[plugins] feishu_oauth_batch_auth: Registered feishu_oauth_batch_auth tool\n[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat, feishu_chat_members\n[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_user_message, feishu_im_user_fetch_resource, feishu_im_user_get_messages, feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages, feishu_im_user_search_messages\n[plugins] feishu_search: Registered feishu_search_doc_wiki\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive_file, feishu_doc_comments, feishu_doc_media\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki_space, feishu_wiki_space_node\n[plugins] feishu_sheets: Registered feishu_sheet\n[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_bot_image\n[plugins] Registered all OAPI tools (calendar, task, bitable, search, drive, wiki, sheets, im)\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_fetch_doc, feishu_create_doc, feishu_update_doc\n[plugins] feishu_oauth: Registered feishu_oauth tool\n[plugins] feishu_oauth_batch_auth: Registered feishu_oauth_batch_auth tool\nOpenClaw status\n\nOverview\n┌──────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Item                 │ Value                                                                                         │\n├──────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Dashboard            │ http://192.168.31.146:18789/                                                                  │\n│ OS                   │ linux 6.8.0-106-generic (x64) · node 22.22.1                                                  │\n│ Tailscale            │ off                                                                                           │\n│ Channel              │ stable (default)                                                                              │\n│ Update               │ pnpm · up to date · npm latest 2026.3.28                                                      │\n│ Gateway              │ local · ws://127.0.0.1:18789 (local loopback) · reachable 105ms · auth token · halei-Surface- │\n│                      │ Pro-4 (192.168.31.146) app 2026.3.28 linux 6.8.0-106-generic                                  │\n│ Gateway service      │ systemd installed · enabled · running (pid 23969, state active)                               │\n│ Node service         │ systemd not installed                                                                         │\n│ Agents               │ 2 · 2 bootstrap files present · sessions 11 · default main active 1m ago                      │\n│ Memory               │ 0 files · 0 chunks · sources memory · plugin memory-core · vector unknown · fts ready ·       │\n│                      │ cache on (0)                                                                                  │\n│ Plugin compatibility │ none                                                                                          │\n│ Probes               │ skipped (use --deep)                                                                          │\n│ Events               │ none                                                                                          │\n│ Heartbeat            │ 30m (main), disabled (tts)                                                                    │\n│ Sessions             │ 11 active · default MiniMax-M2.7 (205k ctx) · 2 stores                                        │\n└──────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSecurity audit\nSummary: 0 critical · 8 warn · 1 info\n  WARN Control UI insecure auth toggle enabled\n    gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth=true does not bypass secure context or device identity checks; only dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth disables Control UI device…\n    Fix: Disable it or switch to HTTPS (Tailscale Serve) or localhost.\n  WARN Feishu doc create can grant requester permissions\n    channels.feishu tools include \"doc\"; feishu_doc action \"create\" can grant document access to the trusted requesting Feishu user.\n    Fix: Disable channels.feishu.tools.doc when not needed, and restrict tool access for untrusted prompts.\n  WARN Insecure or dangerous config flags enabled\n    Detected 1 enabled flag(s): gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth=true.\n    Fix: Disable these flags when not actively debugging, or keep deployment scoped to trusted/local-only networks.\n  WARN Gateway token looks short\n    gateway auth token is 12 chars; prefer a long random token.\n  WARN No auth rate limiting configured\n    gateway.bind is not loopback but no gateway.auth.rateLimit is configured. Without rate limiting, brute-force auth attacks are not mitigated.\n    Fix: Set gateway.auth.rateLimit (e.g. { maxAttempts: 10, windowMs: 60000, lockoutMs: 300000 }).\n  WARN Some gateway.nodes.denyCommands entries are ineffective\n    gateway.nodes.denyCommands uses exact node command-name matching only (for example `system.run`), not shell-text filtering inside a command payload. - Unknown …\n    Fix: Use exact command names (for example: canvas.present, canvas.hide, canvas.navigate, canvas.eval, canvas.snapshot, canvas.a2ui.push, canvas.a2ui.pushJSONL, canvas.a2ui.reset). If you need broader restrictions, remove risky command IDs from allowCommands/default workflows and tighten tools.exec policy.\n… +2 more\nFull report: openclaw security audit\nDeep probe: openclaw security audit --deep\n\nChannels\n┌─────────────────┬─────────┬────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Channel         │ Enabled │ State  │ Detail                                                                          │\n├─────────────────┼─────────┼────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Feishu          │ ON      │ OK     │ configured                                                                      │\n│ openclaw-weixin │ ON      │ OK     │ token unknown (759f…f338 · len 58) · accounts 1/1                               │\n└─────────────────┴─────────┴────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSessions\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────┬─────────┬─────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Key                                          │ Kind   │ Age     │ Model           │ Tokens                           │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┼─────────┼─────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────┤\n│ agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f59…             │ direct │ 1m ago  │ MiniMax-M2.7    │ 35k/205k (17%) · 🗄️ 98% cached   │\n│ agent:main:cron:6b6dfce6-3240-4…             │ direct │ 15h ago │ openrouter/auto │ 32k/200k (16%)                   │\n│ agent:main:cron:6b6dfce6-3240-4…             │ direct │ 15h ago │ openrouter/auto │ 32k/200k (16%)                   │\n│ agent:main:subagent:360f2dcb-f2…             │ direct │ 3d ago  │ openrouter/free │ 46k/200k (23%) · 🗄️ 1670% cached │\n│ agent:main:subagent:64fffe46-20…             │ direct │ 3d ago  │ openrouter/free │ 31k/200k (15%) · 🗄️ 293% cached  │\n│ agent:main:subagent:483330f7-5e…             │ direct │ 3d ago  │ openrouter/free │ 51k/200k (26%) · 🗄️ 2380% cached │\n│ agent:main:subagent:35a36f61-da…             │ direct │ 3d ago  │ openrouter/free │ 30k/200k (15%) · 🗄️ 15% cached   │\n│ agent:main:subagent:db04fc71-d2…             │ direct │ 3d ago  │ openrouter/free │ 42k/200k (21%)                   │\n│ agent:main:subagent:fca6ce70-f3…             │ direct │ 3d ago  │ openrouter/auto │ 23k/2000k (1%)                   │\n│ agent:main:openclaw-weixin:dire…             │ direct │ 4d ago  │ openrouter/auto │ unknown/205k (?%)                │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────┴─────────┴─────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────┘\n\nFAQ: https://docs.openclaw.ai/faq\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting\n\nNext steps:\n  Need to share?      openclaw status --all\n  Need to debug live? openclaw logs --follow\n  Need to test channels? openclaw status --deep"}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"marine-willow","total":112,"totalLines":112,"totalChars":9808,"truncated":false,"exitCode":0,"name":"openclaw status"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774859509905}}
