{"type":"message","id":"2242371b","parentId":"8b447b83","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:34:36.170Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know what command to run in the terminal to get the QR code for WeChat re-binding. The previous command `openclaw channels login --channel openclaw-weixin --verbose` is already running and showing the QR code. But since they're in a飞书 DM and can't see the terminal output directly, they need to either:\n\n1. Access the terminal on the machine where OpenClaw is running\n2. Or I can provide them with the command to run\n\nThe command is:\n```\nopenclaw channels login --channel openclaw-weixin --verbose\n```\n\nBut they need to run this on the machine where OpenClaw gateway is running (halei-Surface-Pro-4). Since this is a desktop system, they would need to open a terminal and run this command.\n\nThe QR code link is also shown:\nhttps://liteapp.weixin.qq.com/q/7GiQu1?qrcode=c1039d257df513e3f2bdd650d562d711&bot_type=3\n\nLet me provide them with clear instructions.","thinkingSignature":"8eefbb9b5d78f3c1b59ce66a25344239a4bd8af0d939edbe394742bbd979c38c"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n在运行 OpenClaw 的电脑（halei-Surface-Pro-4）上打开终端，运行：\n\n```\nopenclaw channels login --channel openclaw-weixin --verbose\n```\n\n运行后会显示二维码，用微信扫码即可。\n\n或者直接用浏览器打开这个链接扫码：\nhttps://liteapp.weixin.qq.com/q/7GiQu1?qrcode=c1039d257df513e3f2bdd650d562d711&bot_type=3\n\n扫码完成后告诉我，我来确认连接状态。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":118,"output":333,"cacheRead":33405,"cacheWrite":13782,"totalTokens":47638,"cost":{"input":0.0000354,"output":0.00039959999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0020042999999999997,"cacheWrite":0.00516825,"total":0.007607549999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774859664311,"responseId":"0619689072de511c4eff985e6edf8d9d"}}
